[21:09:29] [Render thread/INFO] (Minecraft) [System] [CHAT] §6§oHow to use Gilded Banishment
[21:09:29] [Render thread/INFO] (Minecraft) [System] [CHAT] §6§o--
[21:09:29] [Render thread/INFO] (Minecraft) [System] [CHAT] §6§oYou must first have a Gilded Banisher. Once you have that item, hitting someone has a 25% chance to inflict Death’s Mark. When someone is under Death’s Mark, and they get hit with your gilded banisher at 3.5 Hearts or lower, they will receive Pending Death. 
[21:09:29] [Render thread/INFO] (Minecraft) [System] [CHAT] §6§o--
[21:09:29] [Render thread/INFO] (Minecraft) [System] [CHAT] §6§oOnce Pending Death is applied, your objective will be marked as complete. Pending Death will either go off after time, or go off as soon as they get killed, so watch out for the bomb that comes after you kill them.
